data.description: Looking for a home with a huge SHOP & RV STORAGE?  This home has both!  And this house has a fantastic split floor plan with 4BR/2BA down plus a Bonus Room upstairs!  The spacious kitchen features a Large Eat-In Area (great for entertaining), Granite Countertops with Breakfast Bar, Gas Stove, Walk-in Pantry, and the Refrigerator STAYS! The Primary Bedroom has a beautiful triple tray ceiling, Custom Tiled Shower, Jetted Tub, Private Water Closet, and a Great Closet!  Covered patio/deck backs to greenspace!  The foam-insulated and heated shop measures a huge 24.7' x 37.75'!  Adjacent covered RV storage with electrical hookup measures 17.8' x 43.75'.  There's lots of parking space in the driveway for all of your family and friends to come visit!  Newly installed solar panels virtually eliminate the electric bill!! Gas Stove and Fireplace are Propane-fueled. Make this one yours!!  Agents see remarks!
